text:
**Perfect!** 🇩🇰

Danish is now fully supported! The translation works beautifully:

- **English**: "Hello, how are you?"
- **Danish**: "Hej, hvordan går det?"

I've added **26 additional languages** to your DeepL clone, including:

🇪🇺 **European Languages**: Danish, Dutch, Swedish, Norwegian, Finnish, Polish, Czech, Hungarian, Romanian, Bulgarian, Croatian, Slovak, Slovenian, Estonian, Latvian, Lithuanian, Greek, Turkish, Ukrainian

🌍 **Other Languages**: Hebrew, Hindi, Thai, Vietnamese, Malay, Indonesian, Filipino

Your translator now supports **38 languages total** (including auto-detect), making it much more comprehensive than the original 12 languages!

You can now:
- Select Danish from the language dropdown in your browser at `http://localhost:3000`
- Translate to/from Danish and all the other newly added languages
- Use auto-detection with any of these languages

The qwen-mt-turbo model handles all these languages very well! 🚀
